<div class="container work-content work-maker">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
			<p>
				The first time I had a <em>'aha!'</em> moment in respect to my artistic ability was when I was four years old and drew a spitting image of Donald Duck <em>(pun intended, oh yes!)</em>. Later in life, I worked at Disneyland working as a portrait artist. This served as a loose fundraiser for my art schooling.
			</p>
			<div class="group-vertical-margin">
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
						<%= image_tag 'art/art-giraffe.jpg', class: "img-responsive work" %>
					</div>
					<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 hidden-xs">
						<%= image_tag 'art/art-eagle.jpg', class: "img-responsive work" %>
					</div>
					<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
						<%= image_tag 'art/art-rabbit.jpg', class: "img-responsive work" %>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
						<%= image_tag 'art/art-james.jpg', class: "img-responsive work" %>
					</div>
					<div class="hidden-xs col-sm-6">
						<%= image_tag 'art/art-still-life.jpg', class: "img-responsive work" %>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	

	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
			<%= link_to "https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/pattycreates/", target: "blank" do %>
				<button class="callout-link">
					View More on Instagram <i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i>
				</button>
			<% end %>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>